  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>ApiVersion</TypeRef> constructor creates a version value used to describe a renderer plugin target API version.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[ApiVersion();
ApiVersion(uint32_t major, uint32_t minor);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="uint32_t" Name="major">
          The major API version number.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="uint32_t" Name="minor">
          The minor API version number.
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
